<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Table present.</p>
<p>Sample response:</p>
<p>In the fives column:</p>
<ul>
      <li>The ones place alternates 0 and 5.</li>
      <li>The tens place changes after every two counts.</li>
    </ul>
<p>In the twos column:</p>
<ul>
      <li>The ones place counts 0, 2, 4, 6, 8, then repeats.</li>
      <li>The tens column changes after 5 counts.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


